      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from a single production lot. Full traceability to device history records maintained. Coefficient of variation for stiffness 8.3%, yield force 9.1%, force at 40 mm 10.2% — all within the 15% acceptance threshold. Constructs distributed across two independent test laboratories to assess inter-laboratory variability."
