      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of clinically relevant loading scenarios; at minimum two displacement rates and two construct configurations tested.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single displacement rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717 protocol and a single construct configuration (standard 45 mm rod span). Clinical use encompasses varied loading rates and construct geometries. This factor does not meet the required level; however, the single test condition is consistent with regulatory submission precedent and the quasi-static nature of the simulation. Accepted as a documented limitation with compensating evidence from literature."
    },
    {
