      "rationale": "One-to-one correspondence established between FEA model and physical test specimens via CMM measurements and certified material reports. Boundary condition equivalency verified by comparing measured fixture compliance against modeled fixture stiffness (difference < 2%). Torque applied to set screws replicated in FEA via pretension elements with measured torque values."
