    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted based on regulatory precedent for ASTM F1717 single-condition testing and compensating evidence from published literature. Quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%) satisfied for all three QoIs across all 11 constructs at both test laboratories. The FEA modeling framework is deemed credible for the stated COU.",
